plot: Nombre Original: Ricky Gervais Live Show - PoliticsDirector: Ricky GervaisActores: Ricky GervaisPolitics is the second of Ricky Gervais' stand-up shows. It was written and performed by the comedian Gervais. As the title suggests the show takes the political sphere as its central theme. Gervais toured the show in 2004 and it is now available on DVD.
